-- Kazakhstan's Aug inflation up 0.4 pct m/m, 7.1 pct yr/yr
-- By Mariya Gordeyeva
-- Tue Sep 02, 2014 12:14AM EDT
-- None



ALMATY, Sept 2 (Reuters) - Kazakhstan's monthly consumer price inflation accelerated to 0.4 percent in August from 0.1 percent in July, the State Statistics Agency said on Tuesday.

